<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='895000' id='t-895000'>So I'd like to leave you with two thoughts.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='897000' id='t-897000'>There's been a sea change in aid, from top-down mega-projects</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='902000' id='t-902000'>to bottom-up, grassroots, micro-finance investing in the roots,</span>
